<div class="title">Eat All the Cactus</div>
<div class="substance">Cacti - T. peruvianus</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Paul+C.&Exact=1">Paul C.</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Paul C.. "Eat All the Cactus: An Experience with Cacti - T. peruvianus (exp19241)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 4, 2002. erowid.org/exp/19241</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
